title: Clicgear Double-Canopy 68” Wind Resistant Umbrella for Sun and Rain
features: Protects you from the rain or sun
Universally fits all golf push carts with umbrella holders
Custom molded handle designed to fit perfectly in all Clicgear umbrella holders
Vented double canopy allows air to flow through and helps prevent the umbrella from inverting from gusts of wind
description: The Clicgear Umbrella is a perfect complement to your Clicgear or Rovic cart. The handle is molded to specifically fit all Clicgear umbrella mounts. The Clicgear Umbrella will also fit any golf push-pull cart with an umbrella holder. With an oversized, double canopy and UV coated nylon construction, the Clicgear Umbrella is perfect for all weather conditions. Rain or shine the Clicgear Umbrella has your back.
